headline: Wall Street banks, crypto leaders set to meet in Washington with landmark Clarity Act hanging in the balance
summary: Wall Street banks and crypto leaders, notably Coinbase, will meet in D.C. on Monday to hammer out details of the latest signature piece of crypto legislation.
